parameters.name: TaskId
parameters.description: Task ID. For how to obtain the Task ID, see [ListTasks](~~454662~~).

parameters.name: TenantId
parameters.description: Tenant ID. For how to obtain the Tenant ID, see [ListTenants](~~454649~~).

parameters.name: WorkNodeId
parameters.description: Work node ID, workflow sequence starting from 0. For example, in Labeling-QC-Acceptance, Labeling is 0, QC is 1, and Acceptance is 2.
